Back to Kings 2023

  • 14 August, 2023
  • Short Videos

Thank you for joining us at Back to Kings 2023.

It was a beautiful day as the Old Boys Union, Family and Friends Association and families of Kings came together to show their support and reminisce. As Kings played against St Josephs College on home soil, it was wonderful to witness our community come together and enjoy the Kings spirit.

Congratulations to each of our teams for their determination and dedication to their sport, and thank you to everyone who came to watch, cheer and encourage our boys.

We hope you enjoy this video from the day.
